an all-new on-device Dictation experience

246
00:15:37,938 --> 00:15:41,875
that lets you fluidly move
between voice and touch.

247
00:15:41,909 --> 00:15:43,710
Let's take a look.

248
00:15:43,744 --> 00:15:47,648
