264
00:16:48,108 --> 00:16:51,044
Now shortcuts work with zero setup

265
00:16:51,078 --> 00:16:54,615
so you can use Siri to get things done
with supported apps.

266
00:16:54,648 --> 00:16:59,386
Now let's talk about another feature
powered by intelligence: Live Text.

267
00:16:59,419 --> 00:17:01,154
Live Text is so useful

268
00:17:01,188 --> 00:17:04,424
because it's deeply integrated
across the entire OS,

269
00:17:04,458 --> 00:17:08,095
letting you interact with text
in images across the system,

270
00:17:08,128 --> 00:17:12,499
from Camera and Safari
to Notes and Screenshots.

271
00:17:12,533 --> 00:17:16,270
And this year, we're excited
to take this integration further

272
00:17:16,303 --> 00:17:18,839
by bringing Live Text to video.

273
00:17:18,872 --> 00:17:23,310
Now you can pause a video
on any frame and interact with text

274
00:17:23,343 --> 00:17:25,812
just like you can today with photos.

275
00:17:25,846 --> 00:17:28,448
It's great for copying code samples.

276
00:17:28,482 --> 00:17:33,453
We're also accelerating the things you do
with Live Text with quick actions.

277
00:17:33,487 --> 00:17:36,690
So now you're just a tap away
from converting currency

278
00:17:36,723 --> 00:17:38,659
and translating a foreign language.

279
00:17:38,692 --> 00:17:42,162
And for an even richer
translation experience,

280
00:17:42,196 --> 00:17:45,532
you'll be able to use Live Text
while in the Translate app,

281
00:17:45,566 --> 00:17:47,701
with our new camera view.

282
00:17:47,734 --> 00:17:50,838
This will be great for when you have
lots of text to translate.

283
00:17:50,871 --> 00:17:55,676
And for developers, we're also excited
to announce a Live Text API.

284
00:17:55,709 --> 00:17:59,613
Soon you will be able to grab text
straight from photos

285
00:17:59,646 --> 00:18:02,216
and videos in apps like Vimeo.

286
00:18:02,249 --> 00:18:05,152
And photos are about more than just text.

