pets, landmarks, plants, and more,

289
00:18:13,227 --> 00:18:16,897
and gives you rich information
about what's in your images.

290
00:18:16,930 --> 00:18:21,134
And this year we have a new feature
that takes image understanding further.

291
00:18:21,969 --> 00:18:25,472
