and place it in apps like Messages.

293
00:18:29,943 --> 00:18:31,979
It feels like magic.

294
00:18:32,012 --> 00:18:34,982
It's actually the product
of an advanced machine learning model

295
00:18:35,015 --> 00:18:37,251
which is accelerated by CoreML

296
00:18:37,284 --> 00:18:40,487
and the Neural Engine to perform
40 billion operations

297
00:18:40,521 --> 00:18:42,055
in just milliseconds.

298
00:18:42,089 --> 00:18:46,660
Together, Live Text and Visual Look Up
continue to unlock

299
00:18:46,693 --> 00:18:50,564
rich and useful information
from your photos and videos

300
00:18:50,597 --> 00:18:54,168
across iOS, iPadOS, and macOS.

