00:35:03,737 --> 00:35:06,006
Now, the smart home is still
in its early days,

580
00:35:06,039 --> 00:35:08,575
and we want to help bring
these powerful experiences

581
00:35:08,609 --> 00:35:10,511
to as many homes as possible.

582
00:35:11,278 --> 00:35:14,147
In order to build a connected
ecosystem at home,

583
00:35:14,181 --> 00:35:16,617
it's important that you have
the most choice

584
00:35:16,650 --> 00:35:19,253
so you don't have to worry
about what works with what.

585
00:35:19,286 --> 00:35:22,923
With that in mind, we joined forces
with other industry leaders

586
00:35:22,956 --> 00:35:25,792
to create a new smart home
connectivity standard.

587
00:35:25,826 --> 00:35:27,794
It's called Matter.

588
00:35:27,828 --> 00:35:32,533
Matter enables smart home accessories
to work together across platforms.

589
00:35:32,566 --> 00:35:34,968
And to ensure we stayed true
to our values,

590
00:35:35,002 --> 00:35:37,905
we contributed HomeKit,
our smart home framework,

591
00:35:37,938 --> 00:35:40,374
as a foundation of this new standard,

592
00:35:40,407 --> 00:35:42,576
so it's built on the same core principles

593
00:35:42,609 --> 00:35:45,712
and maintains
the highest level of security.

594
00:35:45,746 --> 00:35:48,882
Industry-leading brands have
already committed to supporting Matter,

595
00:35:48,916 --> 00:35:53,754
with over 130 products in the pipeline,
and that's just the beginning.

596
00:35:53,787 --> 00:35:56,523
The Matter standard provides
the underlying foundation

597
00:35:56,557 --> 00:36:01,495
to connect smart home accessories,
and it allows us to innovate on top of it.

598
00:36:01,528 --> 00:36:02,796
We take privacy further,

599
00:36:02,829 --> 00:36:06,433
ensuring that data about how you use
your accessories is processed

600
00:36:06,466 --> 00:36:10,804
and stored by default in a way
that even Apple can't see.

601
00:36:10,838 --> 00:36:14,508
With Matter, we can continue to create
amazing experiences in the Home app

602
00:36:14,541 --> 00:36:17,277
while also making sure
all your different accessories

603
00:36:17,311 --> 00:36:20,380
are consistently simple to set up
and easy to use.

604
00:36:20,414 --> 00:36:23,217
And now that you’ll have more
accessory options to choose from,

605
00:36:23,250 --> 00:36:25,853
let's check out how we made
the experience even better

606
00:36:25,886 --> 00:36:27,754
with an all-new Home app.

607
00:36:27,788 --> 00:36:32,059
We reimagined it from the ground up
starting with the underlying architecture

608
00:36:32,092 --> 00:36:34,228
so it's more efficient and reliable,

609
00:36:34,261 --> 00:36:37,264
especially for homes
with many accessories.

610
00:36:37,297 --> 00:36:41,301
We also completely redesigned
how you navigate, organize,

611
00:36:41,335 --> 00:36:45,639
