to see any additional cameras.

624
00:37:27,548 --> 00:37:30,817
We also redesigned tiles
so that different accessories

625
00:37:30,851 --> 00:37:33,987
are more visually recognizable
through shape and color.

626
00:37:34,021 --> 00:37:37,057
And with the new widgets
on the Lock Screen, it's easier than ever

627
00:37:37,090 --> 00:37:38,825
to see how your home is doing.

628
00:37:38,859 --> 00:37:43,997
So that's the all-new Home app,
