1791
01:45:50,617 --> 01:45:53,921
our next generation of Apple Silicon.

1792
01:45:53,954 --> 01:45:57,457
Along with a powerful new
13-inch MacBook Pro,

1793
01:45:57,491 --> 01:46:00,427
